      <name>Quan Dou</name>
    </author>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<p>Zotero syncing has two parts: data syncing and file syncing. Data syncing will share everything except attachment files between your local computer(s) and the Zotero servers. It is free and unlimited (as long as you have a Zotero account). File syncing will share any attached files. There is a storage limit of 300 MB per user. I have been using Box as WebDav for syncing my files. However, Box announced <a href="https://support.box.com/hc/en-us/articles/360052806073-Announcing-end-of-life-for-Box-WebDAV-support" title="" target="_blank">EOL</a> for WebDav support effective April 28, 2023.</p><p>Now I am using a symlink to sync only the <code>storage</code> directory from my Zotero data directory using the OneDrive sync service. This will sync all attachments without corrupting the main Zotero SQLite database.</p><h2 id="OneDrive-Setup"><a href="#OneDrive-Setup" class="headerlink" title="OneDrive Setup"></a>OneDrive Setup</h2><p>Create a Zotero folder in your OneDrive directory, such as <code>D:\OneDrive\Zotero</code> on Windows or <code>/Users/&lt;username&gt;/OneDrive/Zotero</code> on MacOS.</p><h2 id="Zotero-Setup"><a href="#Zotero-Setup" class="headerlink" title="Zotero Setup"></a>Zotero Setup</h2><p>Open Zotero Sync Preferences, <strong>check the two options in Data Syncing and uncheck the two options in File Syncing</strong>. The default Zotero data directory should be <code>C:\Users\&lt;username&gt;\Zotero</code> on Windows or <code>/Users/&lt;username&gt;/Zotero</code> on MacOS. Manually copy the entire <code>storage</code> folder in this directory to the OneDrive Zotero folder. Delete the original <code>storage</code> folder in the Zotero data directory.</p><h2 id="Create-Symlink"><a href="#Create-Symlink" class="headerlink" title="Create Symlink"></a>Create Symlink</h2><p>Create symlink using the following command:</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><figcaption><span>Windows PowerShell</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$link</span> = <span class="built_in">New-Item</span> `</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">-ItemType</span> SymbolicLink `</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">-Path</span> <span class="string">&quot;D:\OneDrive\Zotero\storage&quot;</span> `</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">-Target</span> <span class="string">&quot;C:\Users\&lt;username&gt;\Zotero\storage&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><figcaption><span>MacOS Terminal</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ln</span> -s <span class="string">&quot;/Users/&lt;username&gt;/OneDrive/Zotero/storage&quot;</span> <span class="string">&quot;/Users/&lt;username&gt;/Zotero/storage&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]>
    </content>
